---
description: Image import guidelines for React/Gatsby projects
globs: ["**/*.js", "**/*.jsx", "**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Always import images using ES6 imports (import imageName from 'path/to/image.png')
Never use direct src paths like "/src/images/image.png" as they won't work in bundled builds

Examples:
✅ Correct: import logo from '../../images/logo.png'; then use src={logo}
❌ Wrong: src="/src/images/image.png"
